:47:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FYpORT_8M2g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFYpORT_8M2g&d=oa%2BbSijZO%2BDWYSsAyiffbhF66oQwccw1TbdUPfwT%2FAY%3D&h=6e71c496\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FYpORT_8M2g</a>"},{"pid":"e15772578e5e054bb37d3fe9dc40816e8d07b35f","tid":2088245,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T06:50:45.000Z","msg":"但中國並不是蘇聯：除了史無前例地成功結合了列寧主義和資本主義之外，更重要的是中共從蘇聯解體中，系統性地汲取了教訓，從而避免了同樣的命運<br />\n<br />\n係呀<br />\n恐怕支那會死得更慘<br />\n支共黨員好似朱明後代咁被人屠殺"},{"pid":"ab9eb931c63de6e1faa46b03406168c211f29e5d","tid":2088245,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0d4313384ca890cea0bbb0de52d25d154e7e06b","tid":2088245,"uid":275570,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T06:27:45.000Z","msg":"愚公移成日鬧李柱銘係港奸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n顧惦自己個仔先啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T06:51:44.000Z","msg":"李柱銘真垃圾"},{"pid":"9688bcf2f80ccb18bab8a75e397536350240b863","tid":2088245,"uid":54959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T07:11:26.000Z","msg":"俾佢咁講完，更加明如果拜登當選代表咩事"}]}